OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFlight cancellations:      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChildren and teachers      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstranded abroad as school  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ben, 17, was due home on Saturday in   
OL,6, plenty of time to take his maths GCSE  
OL,7, on Tuesday, but after a cancelled      
OL,8, flight and a frantic scrabble for train
OL,9, tickets, he'll only just make it.      
OL,11,FA week of flight cancellations and     
OL,12,Fdelays have upended the plans of       
OL,13,Fhundreds of school pupils and some     
OL,14,Fteachers who have been on holiday.     
OL,16,FAs a result, many will miss Monday     
OL,17,Fmorning's start of the new half-term.  
OL,19,FAnd some, like Ben, are facing an      
OL,20,Fanxious journey home.                  
